    "Product Content and Description Creation 4.4.1.",
    "Automated, brand-consistent product copywritingCreating unique product descriptions in great numbers is an ongoing work.",
    "But with appropriately written prompts and LLMs, companies might automate this process while keeping brand consistency in tone and style.",
    "One cue may guide the model to generate material in a \"luxurious tone,\" \"playful and eccentric voice,\" or \"SEO-optimized format,\" as needed.",
    "It ensures that every product page is painstakingly created instead of being furnished with generic material."
  ],
